Northgate Exploration Ltd, dem talk sey e dey propose to amalgamate four of im associated companies.

Under one plan wey de talk sey dem go do two step by step, ABM Gold Corp, one gold exploration, and management company, dem go merge wit Neptune Resources Corp, United Gold Corp, and Inca Resources Inc.

Abm go still increase im stake for Sonora Gold Corp to 42% from 26%.

Nngate yarn sey na about 50% of di equity, and 81% of di vote of ABM after di amalgamation.

Di amalgamation na subject of regulatory approval, and na part of the shareholders of ABM, Inca, United and Novune for special meeting on November 10.

